Privacy Policy
Punch Time Clock ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information related to your use of our mobile application ("App").
1. Information We Collect
We do not collect personally identifiable information unless voluntarily provided by the user. The types of information we collect include:
App Usage Data
: We use Firebase Analytics (without AdID support) to gather insights into how users interact with the App. This includes general usage patterns and engagement levels.
Crash and Performance Data
: Firebase Crashlytics helps us identify and diagnose issues within the App by collecting crash reports and performance metrics.
Feedback Submissions
: Users may voluntarily submit feedback through a form in the App. This may include:
Email address (optional)
Device type, iOS version, app version, and other technical details
2. How We Use Your Information
The collected information is used to:
Monitor app performance and improve functionality
Diagnose and fix bugs and crashes
Enhance the user experience based on engagement trends
Respond to user feedback when an email address is provided (optional)
3. How We Share Your Information
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. Limited information may be shared with third-party services strictly for app functionality, including:
Google Firebase
: For analytics, crash reporting, and feedback storage
4. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect collected data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no digital system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
5. User Rights
You have the right to:
Disable analytics tracking through your device settings or opt out of feedback submission.
Contact us to request the deletion of voluntarily submitted feedback containing your email.
6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will be available on our website.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at punch@trentmorris.com.
Last Updated: March 14, 2025